Database File License Notice
These database files are intended to be used together with the original Lite Catalog application.
Use of these files within the Lite Catalog application is allowed without additional permission.
Use of these database files with other applications, software, services, or systems is not permitted without prior permission from the author.
Modification, redistribution, or repackaging of the database files for use in other software products also requires explicit approval from the author.
The icons located in the "icons" folder of each category belong to the respective owners of the applications they represent. These icons are included solely for the purpose of visual identification and easier navigation to those applications.
All trademarks, logos, and application names remain the property of their respective owners.

